<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 02:06:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着人工智能电力需求飙升，陷入困境的比特币矿工的一个亮点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-25/bitcoin-btc-miners-help-electric-grid-as-ai-data-centers-boom</link><description>矿工可以为电网带来好处。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.V9vyUYcOXY/v22/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-25/bitcoin-btc-miners-help-electric-grid-as-ai-data-centers-boom</guid></item><item><title>迈克尔·塞勒失败的融资模式震惊了比特币交易者</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/michael-saylor-s-misfiring-funding-model-jolts-bitcoin-traders</link><description>对迈克尔·塞勒(Michael Saylor)的比特币购买机器开始失灵的担忧正在席卷整个加密货币市场，加剧了比特币的最新一轮抛售，并暴露了过去两年支撑全球最大加密货币需求的金融结构之一的裂缝。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i7p5zlwaJy68/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 17:13:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/michael-saylor-s-misfiring-funding-model-jolts-bitcoin-traders</guid></item><item><title>比特币价值 100 亿美元的期权到期风险加剧抛售</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/bitcoin-s-woes-could-be-compounded-by-10-billion-options-expiry</link><description>比特币正面临大规模期权到期，这可能会给已经在机构需求减弱和宏观经济逆风中苦苦挣扎的市场带来更大压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i14rCG_hn7z4/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 04:39:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/bitcoin-s-woes-could-be-compounded-by-10-billion-options-expiry</guid></item><item><title>Cantor SPAC 和 Adam Back DAT 之间的加密交易被推迟</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/crypto-deal-between-cantor-spac-and-adam-back-dat-gets-delayed</link><description>备受关注的关于坎托·菲茨杰拉德关联公司与亚当·巴克领导的数字资产财务公司之间合作的投票已被推迟。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/isCQTjUduxkE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 21:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/crypto-deal-between-cantor-spac-and-adam-back-dat-gets-delayed</guid></item><item><title>最大的加密货币买家望而却步，比特币再次跌破 60,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-breaks-60-000-again-as-crypto-s-biggest-buyers-wobble</link><description>比特币跌回 60,000 美元以下，重新引发了过去两年加密货币领域基本没有的担忧：当市场最大买家面临压力而散户交易者失去兴趣时，会发生什么。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJOvnMXh864o/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 18:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-breaks-60-000-again-as-crypto-s-biggest-buyers-wobble</guid></item><item><title>比特币撤退的零售大军暴露出新的脆弱性</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-s-retreating-retail-army-exposes-fresh-market-fragility</link><description>比特币多年来一直试图摆脱其作为投机散户交易者游乐场的声誉。它最近的抛售暴露了这种权衡：华尔街带来了规模和合法性，但曾经帮助吸收急剧下跌的散户买家基本上消失了。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDWGM9hBqFxc/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 12:27:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-s-retreating-retail-army-exposes-fresh-market-fragility</guid></item><item><title>塞勒面临比特币困境，没有简单的出路</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/saylor-s-best-bet-may-be-to-halt-strategy-s-bitcoin-btc-buying-spree</link><description>Michael Saylor 的比特币购买机器 Strategy Inc. 如果想恢复市场对其股票的信心，就应该停止购买这种加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCn0ThsHx9F0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 07:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/saylor-s-best-bet-may-be-to-halt-strategy-s-bitcoin-btc-buying-spree</guid></item></channel></rss>